Package: arronax
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
    ${python3:Depends},
    gir1.2-glib-2.0,
    gir1.2-gtk-3.0,
    gir1.2-wnck-3.0,
    python3-gi (>= 2.90),
    gir1.2-gdkpixbuf-2.0,
    python3-pkg-resources,
    libgtk-3-0 (>= 3.18)
Description: Create and modify application, file and URI starters.
    Arronax is a GTK based GUI program to create and modify starters
    (*.desktop files) for applications, files, and URIs.
    .
    This package contains the standalone version of Arronax. 


Package: arronax-nautilus
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
    arronax,
    gir1.2-nautilus-3.0,
    python3-nautilus | python-nautilus
Description: Create and modify application, file and URI starters.
    Arronax is a GTK based GUI program to create and modify starters
    (*.desktop files) for applications, files, and URIs.
    .
    This package contains the Nautilus plugin for Arronax. It adds a
    "Create starter" menu item to the file context menu in Nautilus


Package: arronax-caja
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
    arronax,
    gir1.2-caja-2.0,
    python3-caja | python-caja
Description: Create and modify application, file and URI starters.
    Arronax is a GTK based GUI program to create and modify starters
    (*.desktop files) for applications, files, and URIs.
    .
    This package contains the Caja plugin for Arronax. It adds a 
    "Create starter" menu item to the desktop's context menu and to the file 
    context menu in Caja


